solution.text:
Looking at the ones place, A X A, must give 9 in the ones digit.
Therefore only two numbers, 3 and 7 can be possible.
A cannot be 7 as \( 111117 \times 37 \neq 7666329 \) .
\(\Rightarrow\) Hence, A = 3, which fits \(111113 \times 33 = 3666729\)
